Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:12.54,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\fs16}I must be dreaming tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:18.28,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\fs16}We erase it from our memories
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:24.97,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\fs16}You can't escape I only know this secret with you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:34.68,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\fs16}How can I protect you forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:40.32,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\fs16}Close your eyes I'll be anything for you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:48.30,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\fs16}I can't live this life without you by my side
