Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.59,0:22:22.75,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}How can I make you know my heart is with you hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.93,0:22:29.35,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}人間は誰も忘れていく痛めた傷跡も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.66,0:22:36.25,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}時の流れ見送る度に薄れる感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.39,0:22:41.68,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}たけどこれ以上見過ごしたくなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:42.25,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Back and forth　心中叫んでやまない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:46.08,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}time over　消えていく残像それは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.14,0:22:51.10,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}あなたそのものだから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.69,0:22:51.27,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}So now that you & I
