Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.65,0:22:58.03,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「I'll believe」孤独も因縁さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:22:58.03,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Yeah，yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.17,0:23:01.60,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}灼熱の記録の欠片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:04.81,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}未来を映すbrightness
